<item>
            <title>[SOLR-13042] Miscellaneous JSON Facet API docs improvements</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-13042</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;While working on &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-12965&quot; title=&quot;Add JSON faceting support to SolrJ&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-12965&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-12965&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; I noticed a few minor issues with the JSON faceting ref-guide pages.  Nothing serious, just a few annoyances.  Tweaks include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;missing/insufficient description of some params for Heatmap facets&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Weird formatting on &quot;Domain Filters&quot; example&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;missing &quot;fields&quot;/&quot;fl&quot; in the &quot;Parameters Mapping&quot; table&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Figured I&apos;d just create a JIRA and fix these before I forgot about them&lt;/p&gt;</description>
